block content
  .row.banner
    .col-12
      h1= title
  .row
    .col-12.col-lg-8
      li: a(href="/about") About Us
      .revcontainer
        h2.revhead About Us
        p.revmsg Welcome to Trendy Treasures, your premier destination for stylish and affordable clothing. Our mission is to provide you with the latest fashion trends and quality garments to enhance your wardrobe. Whether you're looking for casual wear, formal attire, or accessories, we have something for everyone.
      .revcontainer
        h2.revhead Our Story
        p.revmsg At Trendy Treasures, we started with a simple vision: to make fashionable clothing accessible to all. We believe that everyone deserves to look and feel their best, and our curated collection reflects that commitment. From day one, our goal has been to provide a seamless shopping experience, whether online or in-store.
      .revcontainer
        h2.revhead What We Offer
        ul.revmsg
          li Trendy Collections: Explore a wide range of clothing options, from trendy casual outfits to elegant formal wear, designed for every occasion.
          li Easy Online Shopping: Our user-friendly website makes it simple to browse our collections, read reviews, and find the perfect outfit.
          li Quality Assurance: We carefully select each item to ensure high quality and style, so you can shop with confidence.
      .revcontainer
        h2.revhead Our Commitment
        p.revmsg We are dedicated to providing an exceptional shopping experience. Our team continuously updates our inventory with the latest styles and listens to your feedback to improve our services. We are here to assist you with any inquiries or concerns you may have.
        p.revhead Thank you for choosing Trendy Treasures. We hope you enjoy shopping with us and find something that reflects your unique style!
